adopters. The dependent variable is ROI (Return on Investment), which reflects the
profitability of investments made by enterprises. This methodology allows for a deeper
understanding of the complex dynamics between AI adoption and financial performance,
providing more accurate predictions and capturing intricate patterns in the data (Comet,
